Uses of Package
itl.enabler.api

  • Packages that use itl.enabler.api 
    Package Description
    itl.enabler.api
    The core forecourt classes needed by your application to connect to the Enabler
    itl.enabler.api.events.forecourt
    Contains classes needed for handling forecourt events
    itl.enabler.api.events.pump
    Contains classes needed for handling pump events
  • Classes in itl.enabler.api used by itl.enabler.api 
    Class and Description
    ApiResult
    Type for the result of an API method call
    Attendant
    Configured attendant in Enabler
    Attendant.AttendantEventListener
    Event Listener for the Attendant class
    AttendantCollection
    A collection of Attendant objects
    AttendantCollection.AttendantCollectionEventListener
    Listens to events from every Attendant in the collection.
    Clients can either implement this interface to receive events on the whole Attendant Collection or subscribe to events from individual attendantsByNum.
    BlendData
    Blending delivery information
    DeliveryData
    Transaction delivery properties
    EnablerException
    Exception thrown when an Enabler API methods fails, indicating the reason.
